'''Alex (Lex) van Delden''' (21 June 1947 - 6 October 2010) was a Dutch actor and singer. His film credits include ''[[A Bridge Too Far (film)|A Bridge Too Far]]'', ''[[Soldier of Orange]]'' and ''[[Bad Timing]]''. He was the son of composer [[Lex van Delden]].

